### TN3270 API 测试 - 包含字符串输入

### 1. 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/health

### 2. API1: 登录到 TSO 主菜单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/login
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. API2: 输入命令（指定位置，不自动回车）
# 在第 4 行第 13 列输入 "2"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/menu/command
Content-Type: application/json
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

{
  "row": 4,
  "column": 13,
  "command": "2"
}

### 4. API8: 发送字符串（不指定位置，在当前光标位置输入）✨ 新增
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/send/string
Content-Type: application/json
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

{
  "text": "Hello"
}

### 5. API5: 发送回车键
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/key/enter
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

### 6. 获取当前屏幕内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/screen
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

### 7. API7: 发送 Tab 键
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/key/tab
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

### 8. API6: 发送 Reset
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/key/reset
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

### 9. 完整操作流程示例：使用 Tab 和字符串输入
# 步骤1: 输入第一个值（指定位置）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/menu/command
Content-Type: application/json
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

{
  "row": 5,
  "column": 10,
  "command": "VALUE1"
}

### 步骤2: 按 Tab 跳到下一个字段
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/key/tab
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

### 步骤3: 在当前位置输入字符串（不指定位置）✨
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/send/string
Content-Type: application/json
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

{
  "text": "VALUE2"
}

### 步骤4: 按回车提交
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/key/enter
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

### 10. 字符串输入示例 - 输入用户名
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/send/string
Content-Type: application/json
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

{
  "text": "HERC01"
}

### 11. Tab 到密码字段
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/key/tab
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

### 12. 输入密码
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/send/string
Content-Type: application/json
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

{
  "text": "PASSWORD123"
}

### 13. 回车提交
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/key/enter
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

### 14. API3: 执行 LOGOFF
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tn3270/logoff
X-Session-Id: YOUR_SESSION_ID

###
